introduction: Hello, I'm calling long distance from WINONA RESEARCH. We are a national opinion research company and we would like to interview SOMEONE (A MAN OR WOMAN) in your household.

questions.question: First of all, can you please tell me what county you live in?
questions.action: THANK & TERMINATE. SELECT T.1A ON CRT SCREEN.

questions.question: What is your age, please?
questions.if_refused: Can you please tell me into which of these ranges your age falls?
questions.action: CHECK QUOTAS. IF FILLED, SKIP TO Q.3b. THANK AND TERMINATE. SELECT R.2 ON CRT SCREEN.
